  "body": "In order to reject transactions that would go over the max balance of the account we need a way account for virtual balances.\n\nFor example an account with `5` ETH, sending `6` transaction of `1` ETH should result in the 6th transaction being rejected.\n\nThis should be fully optional and enabled by default.\n",
